---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 35
  - Title: The Cloud of Unknowing
    Chapter: XLVI
Tags:
  - Creation=Creation as Play or Sport
---
I trow that whoso had grace to do and feel as I say, he should feel good
gamesome play with him (God), as the father doth with the child, kissing
and clasping, that well were him so!
